description: This hall of fame Sakura purrs with a rating of 93, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 279, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Leverage for East, Leverage for South, and 5 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [279 Votes, Hall of Fame]
